R.J. Reynolds Tobacco Co, aunit of R.J.R. Nabisco Inc &lt;RJR>, said it has formed anexecutive management committee to oversee the company'sworldwide tobacco operations.    Reynolds Tobacco said the committee's members will besenior managers of Reynolds Tobacco Co, R.J. Reynolds TobaccoUSA, and R.J. Reynolds International Inc.    R.J.R. Nabisco is reportedly attempting to form a masterlimited partnership out of its tobacco unit, part of which willbe sold to the public. Reuter&#3;